Steps to Run the Project

1. Setup

1. Copy the MindfulCampus folder to your local system.

2. Open Terminal and navigate to the project directory.

3. Run the following command:

   ```bash
   npm start
   ```

4. Once the project starts, you will be redirected to:
   [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)


2. Usage

Main Dashboard

After starting the project, you will land on the main dashboard.

Typing Example

Go to the Typing-Examples file to see sample text inputs you can try.

Browser Extension

Open Chrome and load the `browser-extension` folder as an unpacked extension.
This will allow monitoring of social media activity (e.g., Facebook, Instagram).

AI Typing Pattern Analysis â€“ Live Demo

Open `typing-demo.html` to view live AI typing pattern analysis.

Crisis Intervention Demo

Open `crisis-demo.html` to explore the **MindfulCampus Crisis Intervention** feature.

